* ``` * * * * __Note__: This is a UI5 Web Component! [Repository](https://github.com/SAP/ui5-webcomponents) | [Documentation](https://sap.github.io/ui5-webcomponents/) * * @since [2.0.0](https://github.com/SAP/ui5-webcomponents/releases/tag/v2.0.0) of __@ui5/webcomponents__. */ const TableGrowing = withWebComponent('ui5-table-growing', ['growingSubText', 'growingText', 'type'], [], [], ['load-more']); TableGrowing.displayName = 'TableGrowing'; export { TableGrowing };
